<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This ontology defines group-specific object instances for the AI Capstone semantic grounding homework and uses OWL reasoning to infer graspable objects."@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/license> <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Group 13 Semantic Affordance Grounding Ontology"@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "g13" .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/" .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "A group-authored ontology for grounding course task objects, task roles, manipulation affordances, and inferred graspability."@en .
<https://hcis.io/ontology/aicapstone/2026/group13/> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Group 13 Semantic Affordance Grounding Ontology"@en .
